Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:12.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城里的人都是粪土
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:17.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:19.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要斩草除根
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:24.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,杀光这个城里的所有士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:03.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,文件和地图之类的 全部都不要放过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:06.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕是稍微潦草一点的笔记也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:09.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1701.6,117)}第六幕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:09.62,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1411.2,241.8)}MEN OF DESTINY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:08.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都要一并带走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:16.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:19.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然真的把城给攻陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:23.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 奥尔米·乳 你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:26.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经连对你吐槽的精力都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:29.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在放弃的话 战争就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:37.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 喂 这是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:39.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是好大的一幅画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:43.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是这个国家——奥尔特的国父
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,创造奥尔特帝国的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:49.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在六十年前突然出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道漂流者还是废弃物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,详细的事情我们也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:59.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,某天他在酒馆出现并煽动群众
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:03.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,凭借着他天才般的演讲技能和人心掌握术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:06.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,掀起了起义的大旗并向首都进发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,根据按照当时的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:11.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「他似乎已经很熟练了」 这样记载的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:16.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后 奥尔特建国后就好像突然自杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:19.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,原因到现在为止也被谜团所重重包围
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:25.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是漂流者的话会认识这个人么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:26.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:29.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个胡须是怎么回事 是在瞧不起人么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:30.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信长先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰久先生把敌兵拽到庭院里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要把他们给斩草 除根了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:40.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什…么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:43.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:47.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰啊 你无论到那里都是那么地正直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 「除根」是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:53.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是全部杀光的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:53.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:56.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看到精灵族的男人以后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,应该也能断定精灵族的女人都是美女了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:02.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,既然定期地把她们给掳走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵肯定会侵犯她们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:08.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情 在城堡攻陷之前不是应该都懂的么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:13.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,斩草除根什么的 你可不能做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:17.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,打从一开始 干那些脏活可都是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就保持着那份正直活下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:25.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,邪门歪道就交给我这个第六天魔王就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 我可是很熟练的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,饶…饶命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,求你放过我们一条生路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道这样会有什么下场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:56.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们让本国知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,保证会让你们全死光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:04:59.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰久先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们放箭吧 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:05.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们杀掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:07.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰久先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:09.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,杀…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:24.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:26.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:31.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前为止 你们可是尽情地玩弄了这些女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:34.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想着仅仅是扔弃武器表示投降就能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:36.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这可就是大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:41.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙 不是一心想把他们给灭绝的么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:45.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就算反被消灭也算是天经地义的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:48.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧 死了之后变成火药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:56.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:59.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明明到目前为止把我们剥削得这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:02.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在轮到你们的时候却来求饶么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:05.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是刚刚被派遣过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都…什么都没做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:17.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经能够起来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:32.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是用尽全力打下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,萨州人还真是健壮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵我都已经给处理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是个不错的光景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:43.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼下这种命令还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:50.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的手早已抹黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:54.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,伊势长岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:55.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK}比叡山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:55.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,延历寺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:57.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,浅井朝仓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,数不尽数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,数…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:06.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情 我才不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:09.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情 与我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:16.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 怎么了 是在打架么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:17.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,并非打架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:25.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是啊 不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:32.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被人揍完之后训斥什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:33.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是令人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,自从父亲大人以后还没有过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:39.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好像还把平手那老头给惹怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:39.66,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,7.8)}注：平手政秀，战国时代的武将。织田信长之子织田信秀的老师。志贺城的城主。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:44.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什么时候 我比父亲的岁数还大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:56.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个人没死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没做啊 什么都
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:02.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,睡那些女人的事情 我没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:06.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他如此坚持说什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:09.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把他杀掉的话 我们就会变得和那些家伙一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个可怜的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:17.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔米·乳 让他揉揉你的胸部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不被射死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把尸体的首级切下来拿去祭奠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:24.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然可恨 但死了以后便成佛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,身体就用来造火药
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:33.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们漂流者的传闻转眼间就传到了周边的村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:37.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者帮助了精灵族的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击了地方官的驻地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:44.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 当被困在地方官城堡里的女精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:46.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都回到了各自的村庄之时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:50.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,令人困惑的传闻转变为了让大家欢呼雀跃的确信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:54.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那些回到各个村庄的女精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:58.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也带回了信长所给的精心准备的土特产
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:01.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,檄文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,檄文的内容真的很有信长的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:08.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是份可以安抚掌控读者心情的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想要国家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:13.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,来加入我们的队列吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:18.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要再次把你们的女人交出去么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:23.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还要让她们被下一任的地方官当成慰安妇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:29.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 他在附件上说明奥尔特帝国已经危在旦夕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:33.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,通过展示在城里找到的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:36.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是多么狡猾的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:41.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后精灵族们陆续响应起义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.40,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(840,376.2)\frz339.5}精灵族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.40,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(684,604.2)\frz340.6}叛乱范围扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:48.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,精灵族的领地逐渐从奥尔特的支配下脱离出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:01.88,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1809.6,109.5)}歌剧
