Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:14.48,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz328.8\pos(597.6,983.4)}与一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:14.48,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz328.8\pos(842.4,709.8)}那须
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.10,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1010.4,695.4)}信长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.10,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(818.4,697.8)}织田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:17.86,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz21.55\pos(1063.2,760.2)}丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:17.86,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz21.55\pos(916.8,469.8)}岛津
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:22.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:25.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这又怎样啊 紫那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:28.99,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(1341.6,1035.9,1254,599.4,0,4500)}睡觉中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:28.99,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(1353.6,1055.1,1254,630.6,0,4000)}现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:28.99,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(1329.6,1057.5,1254,669,0,3500)}请勿打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:29.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 什么 什么漂流者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:34.62,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1579.2,275.1)}奥尔特帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:34.62,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1507.2,348)}帝都威尔利那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:38.13,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1507.2,219.9)}大治藩公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:38.13,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1430.4,279.9)}圣日尔曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:38.13,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1356,159.9)}馆宫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:41.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无论在东还是在西都打了败仗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,并且在北方有迷之军团
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:47.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上精灵族的叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:51.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,算起来 这个国家也是要完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.39,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1572,272.7)}奥尔特帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.39,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1490.4,448.8)}帝都威尔利那 贵族院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 战局一直在变差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 士兵不够
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:01.11,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1636.8,270.3)}总作战会议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:01.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我国四十年间一直都在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:05.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就连后方的驻扎兵都派出去打仗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,物资也是完全不够
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:11.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,本土和附属地区的税收和掠夺也快接近极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:13.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是应该考虑讲和了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么傻话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:18.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是国父大人所想的万年帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:21.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是这个国家的国策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能如此简单就摒弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:30.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好 大家好 迟到了 抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:32.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让你们久等了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:33.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,挺久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日尔曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:41.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,迟到了 迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:43.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,出来的时候被各种事情耽误了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:46.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那一群人妖是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 你说得太大声了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:51.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被听到的话可不知道会被做什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:54.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是圣日耳曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:56.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有帝国的四分之一的巨大贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他是在国父建国之时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,第一位倒戈投靠国父的贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,传闻如果没有伯爵的叛变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔特帝国也不可能建成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,从那以后再也没有人敢对他提出任何意见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:17.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不需要亲自上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:18.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只是随心所欲地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:23.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助了国父…这不是五十年前的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:23.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:27.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人妖到底多少岁了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为我的迟到道歉 我给你们带来了个好消息哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可不要被吓到了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:38.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有往西方战场上运送物资的一些货船队么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:42.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们 有没有什么可以拿来写字的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,写字的东西 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:47.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下 请用我这只口红吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:50.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 请用我这只口红
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 快点给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:57.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说过无数次这条运输路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:12:59.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不太行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:05.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在被发现 然后完全沦陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:06.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:09.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,又被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 那样根本救不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,又有一艘船被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:16.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩下几艘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:17.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:19.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这帮「商人」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮古彬连商业联合的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.96,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1509.6,553.5)}古彬连联合商会 夏依洛克商店舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:34.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,夏依洛克商会狮鹫快递
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:36.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:42.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔特的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:47.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,古彬连特产的鱼兽油脂的滋味如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:49.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,给我吃饱喝足吧混账家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:53.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后拿去当慰问你们小胡子国父的特产吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:55.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,图拉图拉图拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:59.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 那个「图拉图拉图拉」是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是提督教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:06.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,突袭成功后就这样喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:08.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,图拉图拉图拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:11.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,图拉图拉图拉图拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这次也赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:35.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,四面八方都吹起了战斗的号角呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:41.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不应该把东方的联合商会当成敌人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后殖民地发生了叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:51.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,精灵族的殖民地貌似已经高举了叛乱的旗帜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:55.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 精灵族 真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:58.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要管他们 只不过是一些农奴的暴动而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:01.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}更应该重视西方的战况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:02.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:03.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:08.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔特帝国是单方面往周围扩张的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:12.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了叛乱就代表着不仅仅是精灵族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:16.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而是所有的殖民地的不满一起地爆发出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:18.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会像止不住的野火一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:22.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,各处殖民地将像开庆典一样爆发超大型的叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:27.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后叛乱位于向西进军的必经之路上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:31.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,处于西方的国家主力军队就会与本国相隔绝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:34.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊讨厌 这个国家不是已经完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:39.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我忽然想起了些急事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:43.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先回去了 大家继续加油战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:44.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下 怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:51.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了 这样下去不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:54.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便把那个烛台顺回去吧 那张画也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:57.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻联系精灵族的叛乱军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 听说漂流者也参与其中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:02.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那我亲自去接触他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是精灵族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}也请带上我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:16.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:21.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是菲佐纳村的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:22.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是夏拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:26.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟看了那样的信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是精灵族就应该站出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:31.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的村庄也有人不断地加入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:32.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下来一定能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:34.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,挑起这一切的漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都是些怎样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你问我他们是怎样的人 我也不好答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:41.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能说都是些怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:44.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无论这些漂流者怎么样帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都不是精灵族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:48.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些短耳朵的人类对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:49.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能够信任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:53.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可以信任 至少我是这样认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:02.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,该消气了吧 老大不小了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:04.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是曾经的右大臣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:07.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,归根结底 你为什么这么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不是明摆着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:11.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要搞成村长们的合议制啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:13.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这下全都化整为零了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,本来你还能成为国王的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:19.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不懂什么策略
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:22.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不懂别人的脑袋里在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:28.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信 你能完全看透别人的脑袋都在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:32.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你却看不透别人心中所想之事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:35.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的精灵族一定会跟着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:37.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,国王之类的什么都能当
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:41.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 总有一天会把箭头指向我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在不知道哪个寺庙里睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:46.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,醒来的时候已经被火箭所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:50.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想要在这里重蹈本能寺的覆辙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:55.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你能看清人的内心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:57.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是站着说话不腰疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:59.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:02.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,谋反的滋味我已经尝够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:04.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你真经常被别人背叛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟信胜两次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:10.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,胜家和林 浅井 松永两次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:13.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,荒木 波多野 别所 光秀还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:14.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:18.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我决定了的事就一定会去实现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让你成为王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:26.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:27.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把厕所的泥土…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:30.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:35.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要小心翼翼地干哦 不然会被炸飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:38.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,夏拉 你去告诉其他村的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:42.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把厕所和猪圈附近的泥土都搬过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:45.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是有多喜欢粪便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我去问了各个村的工匠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:53.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这个东西太难制造了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:59.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK}堺和国友的那群家伙还真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:02.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,谁可以制作出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:05.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 擅长铁器的矮人族可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:09.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们都比较擅长这方面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:13.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「矮人族」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:19.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是教导你们精灵族箭术的教官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那须资隆与一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:27.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要让不成气候的你们进行最严格的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:30.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们求生不得求死不能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:34.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在说话的前后都给我加上「源氏万岁」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:36.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,源氏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:37.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,来进行不仅是百发百中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:43.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而是以百发万中为目标的猛烈特训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:47.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的 源氏万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:50.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他说话虽然像是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:53.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但认真起来可是又完美又可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:55.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一可惜的地方就是短耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:59.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:02.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那须兄弟十一人之中最小的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:05.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而我又是家族之中最笨挫的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:08.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,说起哥哥们的美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:11.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是踏在地上就会有鲜花盛开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:12.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大海被劈开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金从天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:18.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这种程度都不足挂齿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对是骗人的源氏万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:32.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是萨州的刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:34.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有东西都倾注于这一击之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要考虑这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:37.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:41.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那一击砍偏了或者被躲开了该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:43.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,干净利落地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:46.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黄泉上的先人 都会称赞你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:50.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,精灵族的人不可能学会我的刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:53.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么想都不适合他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:56.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,弓箭倒是很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:20:59.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似全部人都是射箭的天才一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我和村里的工匠…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:07.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这种躁动不安的感觉到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么要到来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:14.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这种感觉 不像是奥尔特的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:18.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么要到来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:22.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,和关原有着同样的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:24.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让人反胃的战争的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找 把他们找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:35.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 吉尔德莱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:39.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这臭味 是漂流者的臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:45.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉 把漂流者都杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:48.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要在无花果结果之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:51.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就让它枯萎殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,
