Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:07.56,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗜血成性的高尚战士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:12.57,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赤く滾る心に刃と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:12.57,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}灼热翻腾的心中之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:19.66,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}無に成る大儀を掲げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:19.66,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高举心无旁骛的大义之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:31.13,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}陽炎は揺れるシンフォニー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:31.13,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}热浪就如晃荡的交响乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:41.14,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}その声　響く三日月夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:41.14,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那歌声 在新月之夜下荡漾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:44.48,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}こんなにくべる炎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:44.48,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如此久久不息的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:46.98,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明けぬ夜は無いと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:46.98,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不存在永不破晓的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:50.98,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}生を叫ぶ衝動 輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:50.98,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}呼喊生存的冲动 闪耀着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:56.15,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Blaze your way 暁の空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:56.15,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开拓你的道路 向着拂晓之空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:23:00.45,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Bloodthirsty Noble Warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:23:00.45,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗜血成性的高尚战士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:05.21,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赤く滲む痛み引き連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:05.21,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}与被染红的痛楚一同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:12.30,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}果てない今日を踏んだ大地へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:12.30,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}冲破无尽的今日 迈向新大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:19.51,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}栄光を歌う peace at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:19.51,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}歌颂荣光 终归和平
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:23.64,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}更なる大儀を掲げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:23.64,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高举更为雄壮的大义之旗
